#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about problem solving. \n"
"\n"
"Every family faces challenges, but when we work together we can deal with problems in an effective and peaceful way.\n"
"\n"
"What a great skill for your teen to learn too!"
msgstr ""
"Maada ya leo ni kuhusu kutatua matatizo.\n"
"\n"
"Kila familia inapitia matatizo, lakini tukifanya kazi pamoja tunaweza kutatua matatizo kwa ufanisi na njia ya amani!\n"
"\n"
"Ni ujuzi mzuri kwa kijana wako kujifunza pia!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How can problem solving help you and your family?"
msgstr "Je kutatua matatizo kunaweza kukusaidia wewe na familia yako?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is problem solving.\n"
"\n"
"We all know that in life there are times where we face problems, and we all know in a way that when we find ourselves in these situations, it is difficult to think of immediate positive solutions.\n"
"\n"
"Therefore, it is important that when we are facing problems we take a pause, we breathe, keep calm and think of problem-solving skills that we may use.\n"
"\n"
"Remember to include our teenagers when we are solving problems. This will help them to become responsible and learn how to solve their own problems in the future."
msgstr ""
"Habari zenu.\n"
"\n"
"Maada ya leo inahusu utatuzi wa matatizo.\n"
"\n"
"Sote tunajua kuwa katika maisha kuna nyakati tunakabiliwa na matatizo, na sote tunajua kwa namna fulani kwamba tunapojikuta katika nyakati hizo, ni vigumu kufikiria haraka ufumbuzi chanya.\n"
"\n"
"Kwa hiyo, tunapokabiliwa na matatizo ni muhimu tupumzike, tupumuwe, tutulie na tufikirie ujuzi wa kutatua matatizo tunaoweza kutumia.\n"
"\n"
"Tunapotatua matatizo tukumbuke kuwashirikisha vijana wetu. Kufanya hivyo kutawasaidia kuwajibika na kujifunza jinsi ya kutatua matatizo yao wenyewe siku zijazo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"As parents, we sometimes think we need to fix every problem by ourselves. And teens can think the same! \n"
"\n"
"By involving your teen, you strengthen your relationship as well as their confidence. Together you can overcome anything."
msgstr ""
"Kama wazazi, kuna muda tunafikiri kwamba tunahitaji kutatua matatizo wenyewe. Na vijana wanaweza kufikiri hivyo!\n"
"\n"
"Kumshirikisha kijana wako, una imarisha uhusiano wenu pamoja na kujiamini kwao. Pamoja mnaweza kushinda kitu chochote."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can problem solving keep your teens safe? It did for @data.characters.media_female_4.name - tap play to hear her story"
msgstr "Je, kutatua matatizo kunaweza kuwaweka vijana wako salama? Ilifanya kwa @data.characters.media_female_4.name - bofya kusikia simulizi yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I did not have a good relationship with my daughter. I was always shouting at her, and she was refusing to go to school.\n"
"\n"
"Only when I started spending One-on-One time with her did I realise she was being bullied at school. We sat down and used the steps of problem solving. We identified the problem and figured out solutions together: ‚ÄúWhat can I do as a parent so you can feel safe and attend school?‚Äù\n"
"\n"
"We agreed I would talk to her teacher to find a way forward. We found the solutions together, and now we are much closer."
msgstr ""
"Sikua na mahusiano mazuri na binti yangu. sikuzote nimekua nikimfokea na yeye alikataa kwenda shule.\n"
"\n"
"Mara baada ya kuanza kutenga muda na kukaa naye tukiwa wawili ndipo niligundua kuwa alikuwa ananyanyaswa shuleni. Tulikaa chini na kufuata hatua za kutatua tatizo. Tulilitambua tatizo na kulipatia suluhisho kwa pamoja: \" Nini nachoweza kukifanya kama mzazi ili ujihisi salama na uweze kuhudhulia shuleni?\"\n"
"\n"
"Tulikubaliana naweza kuzungumza na mwalimu wake ili kupata ufumbuzi zaidi. tulipata suluhisho kwa pamoja na sasa tupo karibu zaidi."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Problem-solving together is an important skill for every family. Let‚Äôs see how @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name and @data.characters.f2_son_15.name handle a problem calmly and find a plan together."
msgstr "Kutatua matatizo pamoja ni ujuzi muhimu kwa kila familia. Hebu tuone @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name na @data.characters.f2_son_15.name wanavyo kabiliana na tatizo kwa utulivu na kutafuta suluhisho kwa pamoja."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name comes back from the market and finds @data.characters.f2_son_15.name at home in a dirty school uniform with a sleeve missing."
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name alirudi kutoka sokoni na kumkuta @data.characters.f2_son_15.name nyumbani akiwa amevalia sale za shule chafu na mkono mmoja wa shati ukiwa haupo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_son_15.name! That uniform is brand new, why did you get it all dirty and torn!"
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_son_15.name! Hizi sale za shule bado ni mpya kwa nini umezichafua na kuchana kiasi hiki!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sorry, @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name. There is this guy at school, he..."
msgstr "Samahani, @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name. kuna mtu shuleni, ali..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Just give me a moment. I am tired and now worried about having to repair this uniform."
msgstr "Em ngoja kwanza. Nimechoka na sasa nawaza kuhusiana na namna ya kurekebisha hizi sale za shule."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sorry, @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name."
msgstr "Nisamehe, @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "(ü§î_thinking_) Take a pause‚Ä¶ just breathe‚Ä¶"
msgstr "(ü§î_anafikiria_) Chukua pumziko‚Ä¶ vuta pumzi taratibu‚Ä¶"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now tell me, what happened?"
msgstr "Sasa nambie, kilitokea nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This boy in class pulled me off my desk and tore my sleeve. He is kicking me every day, and takes my pens and exercise books."
msgstr "Kijana mmoja darasani alinisukuma kwenye dawati na kuchana mkono wa shati langu. Amekuwa akinipiga teke kila siku, na anachukua kalamu zangu pamoja na madaftari."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I am sorry to hear that, but I am glad you told me, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. We need to do something about your uniform though. After we speak, you can wash it and I will repair it. \n"
"\n"
"But first, what do you think we should do about the bully problem?"
msgstr ""
"Pole sana kusikia hivo ila nashukuru umenieleza, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. Tunatakiwa kufanya jambo kuhusiana na sale zako za shule kwanza. baada ya mazungumzo unaweza kuzifua na nitazirekebisha.\n"
"\n"
"Ila kwanza unadhani tunaweza kufanya nini juu na hili tatizo la unyanyasaji?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He makes me so angry, I just want to hit him. Or maybe I should tell my teacher?"
msgstr "Amenikasirisha sana, nataka kumpiga. Au tunaweza kumwambia mwalimu wangu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hmm‚Ä¶ what do you think would happen if you hit him? And what might happen if you tell the teacher?"
msgstr "Hmm‚Ä¶ unadhani nini kitatokea endapo utampiga? Na nini kitatokea kama tukimwambia mwalimu wako?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If I hit him, we might fight and I could get into trouble. If I tell the teacher, maybe the other kids will laugh at me‚Ä¶ Maybe you could talk to the teacher?"
msgstr "Kama nitampiga tutagomban na naweza kujiingiza kwenye matatizo. Kama nikimwambia mwalimu, wenda wanafunzi wenzangu atanicheka‚Ä¶ Labda wewe unaweza kumwambia mwalimu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That sounds like a good idea. I can speak with your teacher or the school ‚Äî they know how to handle this safely."
msgstr "Ili linaweza kuwa wazo zuri. Naweza kuzungumza na mwalimu wako au shule, wanajua namna ya kulitatua hili kwa usalama zaidi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name‚Ä¶ should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Maybe wait, @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm scared the bully will get even angrier. Maybe I can skip school tomorrow instead?"
msgstr "Em subiri, @data.characters.f2_grandmother_role.name‚Ä¶ Naogopa anayeninyanyasa anaweza kukasirika zaidi. Au nisiende shule kesho?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, skipping school won‚Äôt help. You have a right to be safe. Let‚Äôs practise what you can say if he threatens you again ‚Äî something simple and firm."
msgstr "Hapana, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, Kuacha kwenda shule haito saidia. Unahaki ya kuwa salama. Em tuone ni nini unachoweza kusema endapo atakutishia tena, kiwe rahisi na chenye kuonyesha msimamo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Maybe I can say, \"Stop. I don‚Äôt like that.\""
msgstr "Labda naweza kumwambia, \"Hacha. sipendi.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Good. And remember ‚Äî walk away and stand near other children or the teacher. You are not alone."
msgstr "Vizuri. Na kumbuka kutoka eneo hili na kusimama kando ya wanafunzi wenzio au walimu. Haupo pekeyako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*A week later‚Ä¶*"
msgstr "*Wiki moja baadae‚Ä¶*"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How are things going at school now?"
msgstr "Kwa sasa mambo yanaendaje shuleni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It‚Äôs better. The boy stopped kicking me, but he still says mean things."
msgstr "Kwasasa hali ni nzuri. Yule kijana ameacha kunipiga mateke, ila bado ananiambia maneno mabaya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When you face a problem, take a few deep breaths to help you stay calm. \n"
"Then, try to handle the problem using these four steps!"
msgstr ""
"Unapo pata tatizo, vuta pumzi chache ili ikusaidie kuwa mtulivu.\n"
"Halafu, jaribu kutatua tatizo kutumia hizi hatua nne!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "KNOW IT"
msgstr "FAHAMU"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Identify the problem."
msgstr "Bainisha tatizo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SOLVE IT"
msgstr "TAFUTA UTATUZI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Think of possible solutions and what would happen if we used them."
msgstr "Fikiria njia za utatuzi zinazowezekana na kile kitakachotokea kama tutazitumia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TRY IT"
msgstr "JARIBU"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Choose a solution and try it out."
msgstr "Chagua njia ya utatuzi na uijaribu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TEST IT"
msgstr "JARIBU"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Did it work? Great! If it did not work, then try another solution."
msgstr "Je, imefanikiwa? Safi sana! Kama haikufanikiwa, basi jaribu njia nyingine ya utatuzi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Return the phone and save up together to buy a new one"
msgstr "Rudisha simu na tuanze kuweka akiba pamoja ili kununua simu mpya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look what happened - that didn‚Äôt work... Let's try something else."
msgstr "Angalia kilichotokea - hili haikufanya kazi... Ngoja tujaribu kitu kingine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You cannot go out for the next month"
msgstr "Huwezi kwenda nje kwa mwezi mzima ujao"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Uuugh‚Ä¶ that‚Äôs so unfair, I did not do anything wrong!"
msgstr "Uuugh‚Ä¶ hiyo siyo sawa, sikufanya kosa lolote!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When something bad happens, we often get upset and blame. But what our teens really need is someone to help find solutions together. \n"
"\n"
"Listen to them, accept how they see and feel things, and thank them for trusting you.\n"
"\n"
"Teaching your teen how to deal with problems will help them for the rest of their lives. What a gift!"
msgstr ""
"Jambo baya linapojitokeza, mara nyingi huwa tunakasirika au kulaumu. Lakini kile vijana wetu wanahitaji ni mtu wa kuwasaidia kutafuta utatuzi pamoja.\n"
"\n"
"Wasikilize, kubaliana na namna wanavyo ona na kuhisi vitu, na washukuru kwa kukuamini.\n"
"\n"
"Kuwafundisha vijana wako namna ya kushughulikia matatizo itawasaidia wao maisha yao yote. Ni zawadi ya kipekee!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Here are some examples of problems other parents solved with their teens:**\n"
"\n"
"- My teenager does not want to go to school\n"
"- I am worried my teenager will get pregnant or will get someone pregnant\n"
"- I am worried about what my teen does online\n"
"- My teenager is hanging out with bad friends\n"
"- My teenager is lazy\n"
"- My teenager is not doing their school work\n"
"- My teenager might be using drugs"
msgstr ""
"**Hapa ni baadhi ya mifano ya matatizo ambayo wazazi wengine waliyatatua pamoja na vijana wao:**\n"
"\n"
"- Kijana wangu hataki kwenda shuleni\n"
"- Nina wasiwasi kijana wangu atapata ujauzito au atampa ujauzito binti \n"
"- Nina wasiwasi kuhusu ambacho kijana wangu anafanya mtandaoni\n"
"- Kijana wangu ana barizi marafiki wabaya\n"
"- Kijana wangu ni mvivu\n"
"- Kijana wangu hafanyi kazi zake za shule\n"
"- Kijana wangu huenda anatumia madawa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your home activity this week is to teach your teenagers the steps for problem-solving and use them together when a problem comes up."
msgstr "Shughuli zako za nyumbani wiki hii ni kuwafundisha vijana wako hatua za kutatua matatizo na kuzitumia pamoja pale tatizo linapojitokeza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to use the four steps of problem-solving:** \n"
"üí≠ Step 1: KNOW IT (identify problem)\n"
"üìã Step 2: SOLVE IT (identify solutions) \n"
"‚öíÔ∏è Step 3: TRY IT (try one) \n"
"üéØ Step 4: TEST IT (try another solution if this one did not work)"
msgstr ""
"**Kumbuka kutumia hatua nne za kutatua matatizo:**\n"
"üí≠ Hatua 1: BAINISHA (tambua tatizo)\n"
"üìã Hatua 2: TATUA (tambua suluhu) \n"
"‚öíÔ∏è Hatua 3: JARIBU (jaribu suluhu moja) \n"
"üéØ Hatua 4: JARIBU (jaribu suluhu nyingine kama ya awali haikufanikiwa kazi)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you solve one problem together with your teen this week - using the four steps?"
msgstr "Unaweza kutatua tatizo moja pamoja na kijana wako wiki hii - kwa kutumia zile hatua nne?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Working together with your teen will bring so many good outcomes for you both."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri! Kufanya kazi pamoja na kijana wako kutaleta matokeo mengi mazuri kwenu wote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try it out with a ‚Äòsmall‚Äô problem that may come up, so you can see how it works before tackling a bigger challenge."
msgstr "Unaweza, ijaribu kwa tatizo dogo linalojitokeza, ili uweze namna inavyofanya kazi kabla ya kudhibiti tatizo kubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Just remember that when a situation feels overwhelming, it can really help to use the four steps of problem solving with your teen to break the problem down."
msgstr "Hiyo ni sawa. Kumbuka kwamba pale unapohisi kuzidiwa, inasaidia sana kutumia hatua nne za kutatua matatizo pamoja na kijana wako ili kukabiliana na tatizo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We all have problems, but they don‚Äôt define us! You can choose to address challenges and try different solutions together with your teen. \n"
"This shows your teen that they are never alone and gives them a key skill to use at home, with friends, and for life!"
msgstr ""
"Wote tuna matatizo, lakini matatizo siyo tulivyo sisi! Unaweza kuchagua kushughulikia changamoto na jaribu suluhu tofauti pamoja na kijana wako.\n"
"Hii inaonyesha kuwa kijana wako hayupo peke yake na inawapa ujuzi muhimu wa kutumia nyumbani, na marafiki, na maishani!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_son_2.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you make an impact on your community with these skills? Hear @data.characters.media_son_2.name's story"
msgstr "Je unaweza kuleta matokeo kwenye jamii yako kwa ujuzi huu? Sikia @data.characters.media_son_2.name's simulizi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my father introduced the problem-solving steps to me, it helped me with my family, but it also helped me with my friends.\n"
"\n"
"I told my friends about the steps, and now when we are arguing we sit down and everyone comes up with solutions. We then look for the negatives and positives of each solution, and we agree ‚Äúokay let‚Äôs try this one.‚Äù\n"
"\n"
"My friends even took it to their own homes, and it is helping with their families as well!\n"
"\n"
"It is great when others listen to you and accept your ideas even though you are young. We can all bring that harmony with our friends and family."
msgstr ""
"Pindi baba yangu aliponitambulisha hatua za kutatua tatizo, ilinisaidia mimi, familia yangu lakini pia iliwasaidia marafiki zangu.\n"
"\n"
"Niliwaambia marafiki zangu kuhusu hatua hizo, na sasa wakati tunapobishana, tunakaa chini na kila mmoja anakuja na suluhisho. Kisha tunaangalia madhara hasi na chanya ya kila suluhisho na tunakubaliana ''sawa ngoja tujaribu hii moja.''\n"
"\n"
"Marafiki zangu huchukuwa na kupeleka nyumbani kwao, na inawasaidia wao na familia zao pia!\n"
"\n"
"Ni furaha pindi ambapo wengine wanakusikiliza na kukubaliana na mawazo yako hata kama wewe ni mdogo. Sote tunaweza kuleta maelewano na marafiki na familia."

